      <title>维勒鲁瓦称欧洲央行“非常有信心”实现通胀目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/ecb-very-confident-it-will-meet-inflation-goal-villeroy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行“非常有信心”可持续实现 2% 的通胀目标，甚至应该比 9 月份预测的更早实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/ecb-very-confident-it-will-meet-inflation-goal-villeroy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 13:36:22 GMT</pubDate>
