    <item>
      <title>战时医疗创新大幅降低以色列士兵死亡率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/wartime-medical-innovations-slash-israel-s-troop-mortality-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[定制设计的头盔可避免严重的脑损伤。移动血库和战场上的初步手术。狗牌可传送医疗数据。用直升机将伤员疏散到医院，时间以分钟计算。芬太尼棒棒糖可缓解疼痛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/wartime-medical-innovations-slash-israel-s-troop-mortality-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 13:20:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>森特诺称，若风险成为现实，欧洲央行可能讨论进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/ecb-can-discuss-bigger-cut-if-risks-materialize-centeno-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员马里奥·森特诺表示，如果该地区经济面临的一些危险成为现实，可以讨论更大幅度的降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/ecb-can-discuss-bigger-cut-if-risks-materialize-centeno-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 13:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
